{"tid":841530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[接棒] 加息照入市！買家600萬元破頂價進駐兆康苑","createTime":"2018-09-29T15:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T01:43:45.000Z","uid":31320,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"017f073068604f1236aec0dbe3ee1a6c394c7991","tid":841530,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"加息後樓市氣氛觀望，但無阻部分買家積極入市，祥益地產李啟昌表示，屯門居屋兆康苑剛錄高價成交，單位為B座高層6室，三房間隔，實用面積553方呎，今年6月放盤，自由市場價叫650萬港元，雖然減至600萬元易手，但做價仍創屋苑新高，實用呎價10,850元。原業主於2015年以自由市場價398萬元購入單位，持貨3年轉售帳面賺202萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180929/mobile/bkn-20180929173905561-0929_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180929%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180929173905561-0929_00842_001.html&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d97143d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180929/mobile/bkn-20180929173905561-0929_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c04b96511bd0ddef6f3103fd2856104b0ab17db8","tid":841530,"uid":195998,"like":44,"dislike":5,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"呢d 西樓都賣 600萬<br />\n<br />\n硬淡又要發癲了"},{"pid":"3a0ecd33a2b1267ce61d40a6a162ec9749ffb11c","tid":841530,"uid":185945,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"交通方便，差不多啦"},{"pid":"cfb484b577d1199af76f680d1f60bac433ad98c1","tid":841530,"uid":50457,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"個業主投資高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n$40萬首期，鬆綁就賺$200萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747e4fbdfaa42676b44f03a7ae08c4964bae70c4","tid":841530,"uid":31320,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3a0ecd33a2b1267ce61d40a6a162ec9749ffb11c","tid":841530,"uid":185945,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"交通方便，差不多啦"},